OL,3,CAir Fryers - The Healthy Option?
OL,5,FThe Air Fryer Takeover: There are now
OL,6,Fover 20 million air fryers across the
OL,7,FUK, with two thirds of homes owning
OL,8,Fone.
OL,10,FITV's Tonight programme reveals the
OL,11,Fscale of the air fryer revolution in
OL,12,Four kitchens, as figures show that the
OL,13,Fair fryer craze is far from over. A
OL,14,Fstudy undertaken for the programme by
OL,15,Fcampaign group Recycle Your
OL,16,FElectricals found that an estimated 20
OL,17,Fmillion air fryers have made their way
OL,18,Finto our homes, with two thirds of
OL,19,Fadults now owning one.
