OL,3,CAir Fryers - The Healthy Option?
OL,5,FTech journalist Lara Lewington has
OL,6,Fbeen exploring whether they're better
OL,7,Fthan their traditional counterparts...
OL,8,For is it all just hot air?
OL,10,FA specialist cooking instructions lab,
OL,11,FLeatherhead Food Research, found that
OL,12,Fair fryer ownership is increasing by
OL,13,F10% year on year. They also revealed
OL,14,Fthat most homes are typically using
OL,15,Ftheir gadgets to cook meals for two
OL,16,Fpeople. And the percentage of owners
OL,17,Fwho use their air fryer daily has also
OL,18,Fincreased.
