OL,3,CAir Fryers - The Healthy Option?
OL,5,FWith more and more of us now using
OL,6,Fthese counter top gadgets to rustle up
OL,7,Four meals, Leatherhead Food Research
OL,8,Fare on hand to help food manufacturers
OL,9,Fget it right. The team help
OL,10,Fmanufacturers perfect cooking
OL,11,Finstructions, ensuring our food is
OL,12,Fsafe to eat. Their work is now being
OL,13,Fdominated by air fryers: Leatherhead's
OL,14,FHead of Cooking Instructions, Natasha
OL,15,FBurton, told Tonight: "In 2024, air
OL,16,Ffryers became our second most popular
OL,17,Fcooking technique, overtaking
OL,18,Fmicrowaves for the first time."
