OL,3,CAir Fryers - The Healthy Option?
OL,5,FWith kitchens across the country now
OL,6,Fwhirring to the sound of air fryers
OL,7,Fand new models being released every
OL,8,Fmonth, some are beginning to wonder
OL,9,Fhow long this craze will last and what
OL,10,Fimpact it might have. Scott Butler
OL,11,Ffrom Recycle Your Electricals looked
OL,12,Finto how many of these appliances are
OL,13,Fgathering dust, with some shocking
OL,14,Ffindings. They told Tonight a whopping
OL,15,F764,000 air fryers aren't being used
OL,16,Fand a further 1.5 million have been
OL,17,Fthrown away. Meaning over 2.25 million
OL,18,Fair fryers are being unused or
OL,19,Fdiscarded that could otherwise be
OL,20,Frecycled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
