OL,3,CAir Fryers - The Healthy Option?
OL,5,FScott told Tonight: "If you've got an
OL,6,Fair fryer that is still working and
OL,7,Fyou no longer need it try and sell
OL,8,Fthem, try and donate them, definitely
OL,9,Frecycle them because the material
OL,10,Fthat's sat inside of them can do good
OL,11,Fsomewhere else."
OL,13,FHe said that these gadgets might have
OL,14,Frevolutionised our kitchens, but they
OL,15,Fcan go on to make huge changes
OL,16,Felsewhere once recycled; "It's full of
OL,17,Fsteel, aluminum, plastics, sometimes
OL,18,Fceramics, copper, it could be used in
OL,19,Fanything from life saving equipment to
OL,20,Fschool playgrounds to new electricals."
